data.description: Built in 2022 this three bedroom two bathroom home is move in ready! The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining! The kitchen comes with ample cabinet space, tile backsplash, and granite topped island. The LVP flooring throughout the home gives a luxury look and feel with little maintenance. Only moments from Downtown Kings Mountain and multiple grocery stores, the location of this home is both private and convenient. Make an appointment to view this home today!
